# React Patterns

## Components

- Functional components only
- Server Components by default; add `"use client"` only when needed (hooks, events, browser APIs)
- Colocate feature UI under `components/` (e.g. `components/movies/`)

## Data fetching

- Client: TanStack Query hooks from `lib/api/hooks.ts`
- Server: call `searchMovies` / `getMovieByImdbId` directly in RSC or route handlers
- Always render loading, error, and empty states

## UI

- Use shadcn/ui from `@/components/ui/*`
- Compose with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils/cn`
- Use Next.js `<Link>` and `<Image>` for navigation and posters

## Favorites

- Use `favoritesStorageAdapter` from `@/lib/utils/favorites-storage`
- Generic adapter: `createLocalStorageAdapter` in `@/lib/utils/local-storage`
- Validates read/write with Zod; handles JSON errors
